      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Sep 2022 09:56:57 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://example.org/recipes/pizzadough/</guid>
      <description> Activate yeast in some of the water Mix dry ingredients Add yeast and water, mix &amp;amp; knead until &amp;ldquo;smooth&amp;rdquo; Rest dough for 5-10 minutes, slap and fold, repeat as needed Rise until doubled Punch down, form into 4 dough balls Rest, shape, fridge until ready to cook </description>
